company_summary_description:
Desde 1946 la familia Bresso inicia su actividad empresarial en Argentina con la empresa Bresso Hnos., dedicada a la fabricación de implementos para la industria textil proveyendo a las principales fábricas del país (Alpargatas, Grafa, Flandria, entre otras). Dado el contexto nacional y la situación de la industria en general, e impulsados por la energía y visión que los caracteriza, incursionan en el negocio automotriz asociados con Toyota para instalar en la provincia de La Pampa uno de los primeros distribuidores de la marca (TOYOPAMP).

En 1997 nace Bhassa como único concesionario oficial de Toyota en la provincia de La Pampa y más tarde también en el oeste Bonaerense.

profile_summary:
Debido a mi trabajo en una concesionaria de autos, tengo experiencia en ventas de repuestos, atención la publico, tareas administrativas y logística o manejo de stock. los puestos que desarrollo o desarrollé son: asesor de entregas, encargado de repuestos y responsable de unidades.
Tengo conocimientos de programación, project management y computación en general, a razón de mis intereses personales y los años de ingeniería en sistemas, carrera que pienso seguir.
Cabe destacar también que hablo ingles de manera fluida, con el examen CAE de la universidad de Cambridge rendido y aprobado.

company_summary_description:
Verisure is the leading provider of peace of mind and protection to residential and small business customers across Europe and Latin America.  We deliver professionally-monitored security services  to over 5.7 million customers in 17 countries across Europe and Latin America, with a team of more than 29,000 colleagues.

Verisure’s brand family  includes: Securitas Direct in Spain and Portugal (*), AlertAlarm, Dansikring Direct, Falck Alarms, Mediaveil, TeleAtlantic and NorAlarm to name a few! 

Our alarms are the most widely installed home security systems in Europe. A strong focus on quality and service means our customers are among the most satisfied in the industry!

GROWTH

Verisure enjoyed consistent growth over the past 35 years as a result of its highly entrepreneurial and innovative approach to business. We also continue to expand internationally.

- Strong and visionary Management Team and a robust business plan for value creation.
- We are a big company with a start-up mindset,  fast, agile and lean, merit based, high-performance and value-driven

INNOVATION

- We continuously invest more in new innovation to provide effective, intelligent and reliable security solutions.
- Offer a breakthrough product & service proposition: identify, research, develop, test & refine advanced security solutions.
- Develop exclusive hardware and software features.
- Research & Development centers in Madrid, Geneva and Malmö. 
- +1800 Technologists… and growing!

PEOPLE 

Our successful growth is dependent on our talent pipeline. Our People are our business!  We are:
- Passionate in everything we do
- Committed to making a difference
- Always Innovating 
- Winning as a Team
- With Trust & Responsibility

profile_summary:
I am someone who thrives on adventure and embraces life with enthusiasm. Whether I’m skiing down a snowy slope, hiking through stunning trails, or taking on the challenge of rollerskating, I’m always eager to explore new experiences. My sociable nature drives me to connect with others and enjoy life to the fullest. This same spirit extends into my professional life, where I approach my work with unwavering passion and commitment, always giving 100%.

 I feel truly fortunate to have grown up in a family-run funeral business, as it taught me invaluable lessons about the dedication, compassion, and hard work required to genuinely support families in need. This experience has given me a deep appreciation for the care needed to make a difference in people’s lives during important times. Taking on these responsibilities has made me proud of my work and showed me how much my efforts matter.

company_summary_description:
Pagina oficială a Poștei Române, liderul serviciilor poștale și de logistică din România. Din 1862.

Cu o tradiție de 162 de ani, peste 21.000 de angajați și peste 5.000 de subunități poștale, Compania Națională “Poșta Română” ocupă o poziție unică în ceea ce privește dimensiunea, recunoașterea, acoperirea și loialitatea clienților.

Oferim soluții integrate pentru persoane fizice și companii, de la livrări naționale și internaționale, până la servicii logistice și financiare, cu focus pe nevoile business-urilor moderne. 

Mai multe informații găsiți pe site: 
https://www.posta-romana.ro/a50/despre-noi/prezentare.html

company_summary_overview: Compania Națională Poșta Română is the national operator of postal services in Romania. It offers a range of services including mail delivery, rapid courier services (Prioripost), and money transfer services (postal mandate, E-mandat). The company also provides pension distribution and has a real estate portal for renting commercial spaces, apartments, offices, and land. Additionally, Poșta Română issues and distributes cards for social aid payments.
company_summary_seo: Poşta Română este operatorul naţional de servicii poştale şi servicii de curierat rapid (Prioripost), transfer de bani (mandat postal, E-mandat, mandat online), marketing direct (Infadres), drop mail (Postmesager) şi diverse soluţii business. Poşta Română este furnizor unic de serviciu universal pe întreg teritoriul ţării, la tarife accesibile tuturor.

profile_summary:
I am former Human Rights and Solidarity Coordinator for European Students’ Union (Brussels) and former Program Coordinator at the Central European University’s Human Rights Initiative (Budapest). I am an Aspen Fellow (2018), Young Leaders Program (Romania).

I was appointed the Humanitarian Aid Coordinator for the Refugee Task Force Team at Central European University and was awarded at the Romani Gala Women – Human Rights Activism category – 2015 edition. More recently I served as a Monitoring and Evaluating Expert within the “Împreună“ Agency (Bucharest).

I held an Erasmus Mundus MA in Gender and Women studies from the Central European University (Budapest) and University of Oviedo (Oviedo), an MA in Politics, Gender and Minorities studies and a BA in Political Science from the National School of Political Studies and Public Administration (Bucharest). Additionally, I  also directed and performed in the Vagina Monologues play, a play that delves into consensual and nonconsensual sexual experiences, body image, genital mutilation, direct and indirect encounters with reproduction, sex work, and several other topics through the eyes of women of various ages, races, sexualities, etc.

company_summary_description:
Tai Loy es la primera cadena de Stationery en el Perú. Somos los especialistas y líderes del sector de útiles escolares y de oficina a nivel nacional, con 53 años de experiencia ofreciendo la mayor variedad y los mejores precios del mercado.
 
A lo largo de los años hemos desarrollado un sistema comercial que logra atender de forma eficiente y rápida los pedidos de nuestros clientes. Tenemos una gran fuerza de ventas que llega a todo el Perú.
 
En la actualidad contamos con 72 sucursales, 52 en Lima, 2 en Ancash, 4 en Arequipa, 1 en Ayacucho, 1 en Cajamarca, 5 en Chiclayo, 2 en Huancayo y  5 en Ica y nos encontramos en constante proceso de expansión. Tenemos tiendas de formato mayorista, en las que atendemos principalmente a clientes de librerías e instituciones, y tiendas de formato retail o minorista, en las que se atiende a instituciones y al consumidor final.

company_summary_description:
CIBT is the leading global provider of immigration and visa services for corporations and individuals with over 1,600 expert immigration and visa professionals, attorneys and qualified migration consultants located in over 60 offices in 27 countries. 

With thirty years of experience, CIBT is the primary service provider to 75% of Fortune 500 companies. CIBT offers a comprehensive suite of services under two primary brands: Newland Chase, a wholly owned subsidiary focused on global immigration strategy and advisory services for corporations worldwide and CIBTvisas, the market leader for business and other travel visa services for corporate and individual clients.

CIBT is headquartered in Washington D.C.
company_summary_overview: The Company serves all major travel lanes requiring visas from these and numerous other jurisdictions. As the global leader in visa and immigration services, CIBT works side-by-side with its corporate and individual clients in these highly complex and time-sensitive processes. CIBT, which is in McLean, Virginia, employs nearly 1,300 employees across 15 countries worldwide, including the United States, United Kingdom, Germany, Australia, and the Netherlands.
company_summary_seo: Need a visa for travel or passport services? CIBT is the leading visa and passport service provider with over 50 years of experience. Fast. Easy. Secure. Global offices.

profile_summary:
My dream is to impact as many people as I can by teaching the basics of what I've learned in my life. This is why my current position makes the most sense for me, as I am doing what I've always dreamed of. My new challenge is: how can I impact more people? 

One of the biggest questions in Today's society is: What exactly is a good leader? To me: a great leader is one who can lead with many different hats;  one who is poised but fearless; empathetic and only uses sympathy when it applies; one who is determined and can problem solve and not blame; one who can take the back seat, when it's the right time to do so. 

As I continue to grow and learn more about myself, id like to transfer my knowledge to others - the way a great coach should.  My linked in profile, will help me display my journey for the next few years, and help me to understand: Did I become whom I said that I would?

profile_summary:
With a people-centred approach and a strong commitment to people and organisations reaching their maximum potential, I take a strategic yet practical approach to everything I do. My skills consist of communication, system monitoring, HR, people development, project management, business modelling, and employee relations that have propelled a career focused on designing meaningful people strategies and administratively efficient systems. 
I have applied experience in recruitment, training and development, performance management, and policy development. I am committed to continuous improvement and empowering employees. My leadership style values empathy and accountability along with follow-through and achieving results. 
I have a master's degree in project management from Addis Ababa University and am experienced in leading HR and administrative services. I enjoy dynamic environments where I can be a part of the strategic planning process while also taking a human-centred approach to leadership. I have a passion for creating cultures of learning, collaborative relationships, and sustainable impact.

Delta Defense, LLC is the private company that provides Marketing, Operations and Customer Care for the U.S. Concealed Carry Association. The USCCA helps responsible Americans avoid danger, save lives and keep their families safe.

We're one of the fastest-growing companies in America and a favorite workplace in SE Wisconsin.

* Milwaukee Business Journal “Best Place to Work” award 6 years in a row! 
* Named on Inc. 5000 “Fastest Growing Private Companies” list 11 years in a row!
* Milwaukee Journal Sentinel “Top Workplace” award 7 years in a row!
* Top Workplaces USA award in 2022!

We are a fun, fast-paced and rewarding place to work and grow!

Delta Defense LLC is a growing team of innovative, hard-working, fun-loving people who embrace our mission and our culture.
company_summary_overview:
Delta Defense provides marketing, operations and customer care services to the USCCA. 

Delta Defense powers the fastest-growing firearms training cadre in the country, who prepare responsible citizens to safely and legally carry a gun. The best self-defense insurance benefit in America: we arm our members with the ultimate peace-of-mind and complete protection through financial support and legal defense.

company_summary_description:
Northwest Exterminating has multiple service centers that are ideally positioned to service Georgia, Tennessee, Alabama, North Carolina, South Carolina, and Florida. We specialize in treating residential and commercial properties.

Northwest Exterminating is a family-operated business that was founded in 1951. At Northwest, our mission is to create a healthier living and working environment for our customers. We will uphold commitments made to our customers while exercising honesty, integrity, and excellence.

company_summary_description:
At ModWash, our goal is to Make Life Shine. We’re an express car wash with a commitment to quality service, professional car care, and doing good for our communities.

We like to think that with every wash, we’re delivering something special. Driving a clean car feels good, and we want to spread that feeling of pride across every community we serve.
